         The GAslides package
      LaTeX templates for slides
for Georg-August-Universität Göttingen


File:       README
Maintainer: Studiendekanat Mathematik,
            Fakultät für Mathematik und Informatik,
            Georg-August-Universität Göttingen


DESCRIPTION
===========

The GAslides package provides the layout of
Georg-August-Universität Göttingen for slides/presentations.

Copyright (C) 2022 Georg-August-Universität Göttingen


FILES IN DISTRIBUTION
=====================

   BASE DISTRIBUTION:

      README                 This file
      beamerthemeGA.sty      Package source and installation file
      slides.tex             Slides template
      logo-[12].eps/.pdf     Logo files

   DOKUMENTATION:

      GAslides.pdf           User manual


BASIC INSTALLATION
==================

   The minimum requirement to use the package is to have
   'beamerthemeGA.sty' (as well as the logo files)
   in a directory where TeX can find it.

